headline: Cencora Completes Acquisition of Retina Consultants of America
summary: CONSHOHOCKEN, Pa., January 02, 2025--Cencora, Inc. (NYSE: COR) today announced the completion of its previously announced acquisition of Retina Consultants of America ("RCA"), a leading management services organization (MSO) of retina specialists.
